cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the edit distance computation problem between pushdown automata and their subclasses.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of the edit distance computation problem.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with decidability of certain problems related to edit distance computation.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as pushdown automata are a standard model for programs with recursion.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of the edit distance computation problem.
